{"tid":1103097,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【項少龍再現】電影版《尋秦記》貴州開拍 古天樂古裝頭片場打點","createTime":"2019-04-12T07:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T07:34:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"743e9f000633f7d0bec6e1df196ab555420fc4d6","tid":1103097,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"2001年由古天樂（古仔）、林峯主演的劇集《尋秦記》，這部穿越劇令不少劇迷津津樂道，就連古仔自己一直都想開拍電影版。相隔18年，上月在港舉行的香港電影博覽中，古天樂旗下的天下一公司，宣佈《尋》片將以原班人馬，包括古天樂、林峯、宣萱、雪兒、郭羨妮等開拍，令人期待。<br />\n原來電影版的《尋秦記》拍攝大隊，近日已抵達貴州，並低調開拍，今次亦是原班人馬主演。近日在網上流傳相片中，可見當年飾演項少龍的古仔，穿上白色短袖T，外面套上一件戲服，而他頭上束了髮髻，似是古裝造型。見他跟在場一班工作人員傾談拍攝事宜，在旁有工作人員用紙筆紀錄，作為老闆的古仔，事事親力親為。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190412/large/1555052293_6e6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190412%2Flarge%2F1555052293_6e6d.jpg&h=8ff615d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190412/large/1555052291_dbf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190412%2Flarge%2F1555052291_dbf7.jpg&h=845f6a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190412/large/1555052291_7a42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190412%2Flarge%2F1555052291_7a42.jpg&h=9a700de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190412/59480187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F59480187&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8FHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=fb7ab2d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190412%2F59480187&h=f3a53722\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190412/59480187</a>"}]}